metadata.name: Evergreen
metadata.description:
Evergreen by Bonita Symonds  
2480*3508 pixels  
Hand drawn in Procreate

This is a personal piece about my experience as an artist. It expresses my journey and how my creativity remains growing and evergreen through anything. Nothing can take it away from me.  
Creativity is my secret weapon, and it remains glowing and beautiful even after people try and take it away from me. 
It will always resurface.
